::KitKat::

She slowly raised her head and opened her eyes.  She looked and saw 
she was in the CR chamber. She gave a sigh of relief. She thought she 
was a goner for a while.  She looked down and noticed her left arm 
was gone.  She touched the wire exposed stump where her arm used to 
be.  She had seen Stingtra shoot off her own hand and rebuild another 
one.  But KitKat had never lost a limb before and she found it 
disturbing.  She relaxed in the chamber and let it do it's work.  
When she got out, she would try to find a way to replace the arm that 
was lost. At least she hoped she could replace it.
